platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Klei’s knack for building immersive worlds pays off big-time in Invisible, Inc. The techno-future vibe grabbed us from the get-go, and the hours whizzed by as we infiltrated corporations with our team of super-spies. A brilliant stealth game, its open-ended missions let you hack secrets, avoid detection, and use slick gadgets however you like.
